OL,5, An NHS worker was left feeling "sad"   
OL,6, and "incredulous" after bosses sent    
OL,7, staff an email with advice on how to   
OL,8, access food banks.                     
OL,10,FA body that provides logistical support
OL,11,Ffor the health service across Wales    
OL,12,Fsent the email about the cost of living
OL,13,Fcrisis to all its staff in July.       
OL,15,F"It was knowing that people were       
OL,16,Fsuffering, and we're just being left to
OL,17,Fit," the employee said.                
OL,19,FThe organisation said the email was not
OL,20,Fintended to cause offence.             
